highlights.text: Pritam has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. Kesariya is the highest at #4.
Ghodey Pe Sawaar (From "Qala") by Amit Trivedi, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Sireesha Bhagavatula is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 78 spots at #15.
Tu Aake Dekhle by King has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 64 weeks straight.
Radhika by Tanmoy Saikia and STANNiUM is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #46.
